sql:
SELECT AVG(cpu_usage_concurrent) AS avg_cpu_usage_concurrent
FROM performance_metrics
WHERE error_rate > 0.01 AND throughput < 1000;

SELECT description
FROM load_conditions
LIMIT 1;

external_knowledge:
app_id = 0 refers to a specific application for which we want to retrieve performance metrics; 
Performance metrics are used to measure the efficiency and speed of an application; 
Request rate per second and 99th percentile response time under concurrent load are key performance indicators for an application.
